<lb n="0468b15"/><head type="no">No. 1316</head><div1 type="dharani">
<lb n="0468b16"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0468016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說甘露經陀羅尼
<note n="0468017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00057;〕－【三】，＋（唐于闐三藏實叉難陀譯）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0468017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔&CB00057;〕－【宋】【元】【明】，＋（唐于闐三藏實叉難陀譯）【元】【明】</note>
<app n="0468017"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg>
<rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">唐于闐三藏實叉難陀譯</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0468b17"/>
<lb n="0468b18"/><p type="dharani">南無素嚕皤耶<note place="inline">一</note>怛他揭多<note place="inline">去聲<note n="0468018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔呼之〕－【明】</note><app n="0468018"><lem>呼之</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>耶<note place="inline">二</note>怛姪他
<lb n="0468b19"/><note place="inline">三</note>唵<note place="inline">四</note>素嚕素嚕<note place="inline">五</note>皤囉素嚕<note place="inline">六</note>皤羅素嚕<note place="inline">七</note>莎
<lb n="0468b20"/>呵<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb n="0468b21"/><p>右取水一掬&CB00057;之七遍散於空中。其水一渧
<lb n="0468b22"/>變成<note n="0468019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十＝中【宋】</note><app n="0468019"><lem>十</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">中</rdg></app>斛甘露。一切餓鬼並得飲之。無有乏
<lb n="0468b23"/>少皆悉飽<note n="0468020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＋（佛說甘露經陀羅尼）【元】【明】</note><app n="0468020"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">滿佛說甘露經陀羅尼</rdg></app></p><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
